EDF Trading, Mizuho Sign Deal to Market Carbon Credits in Japan

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 
2011-07-19T09:54:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/edf-trading-mizuho-sign-deal-to-market-carbon-credits-in-japan.html
The trading unit of  EDF SA (EDF)  and
 Mizuho Financial Group Inc. (8411)  agreed to co-operate in marketing
carbon permits and credits to Japanese factories and utilities
and other buyers to help them manage price risks, according to
an e-mailed statement sent by EDF.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
 m.carr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alessandro Vitelli at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net  